asgn2Vehicles

Class Car

  • java.lang.Object
    • asgn2Vehicles.Vehicle
      • asgn2Vehicles.Car

  • public class Car
extends Vehicle
    The Car class is a specialisation of the Vehicle class to cater for production cars This version of the class does not cater for model types, but records whether or not the vehicle can use a small parking space.
    Author:
    hogan
